程序包 org.hibernate.validator.internal.engine.valueextraction

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    AnnotatedObject
    A pseudo type variable used to express that the annotated element itself (e.g. a list) has been marked for cascaded validation.
    ArrayElement
    A pseudo type variable which is used to represent constraints applied to the elements of an array.
    ValueExtractorDescriptor
    Describes a ValueExtractor.
    ValueExtractorDescriptor.Key  
    ValueExtractorHelper
    Various utilities to manipulate ValueExtractors and ValueExtractorDescriptors.
    ValueExtractorManager  
    ValueExtractorResolver
    Contains resolving algorithms for ValueExtractors, and caches for these extractors based on container types.
